    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">咒罵</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>SPEAK so as to TRY to CAUSE DIVINE DISASTER FOR someone.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="huang-jingui">
<p>HUANG JINGUI 2006</p>
<p>SACRIFICE 9.</p>
<p>詛，求神加禍於人，強調加禍之義。</p>
<p>[ 口＋兄 ] ，原與祝為一字，後分化出來，專指以言語向鬼神請求降禍於別人。</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>咒罵 is the current modern word for cursing someone.</p>
<p>詛咒 (lit) is a more formal and perhaps a little less aggressive way of referring to the same action.</p>
<p>咒詛 (lit) is a more formal and perhaps a little less aggressive way of referring to the same action.</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
        </div>
    </div>
